    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>1) File -> Invalide Caches (in IDE IDEA)</p>\n\n<p>2) Manually, got to C:\\Users\\\\AppData\\Local\\JetBrains\\IntelliJ IDEA \\system\\caches and delete</p>\n\n<p>JetBrains:\n<a href=\"https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544519-Directories-used-by-the-IDE-to-store-settings-caches-plugins-and-logs\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544519-Directories-used-by-the-IDE-to-store-settings-caches-plugins-and-logs</a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
